(1435, '_transient_dash_88ae138922fe95674369b1cb3d215a2b', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/12/clifford/''>WordPress 4.4 “Clifford”</a> <span class="rss-date">December 8, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">Version 4.4 of WordPress, named “Clifford” in honor of jazz trumpeter Clifford Brown, is available for download or update in your WordPress dashboard. New features in 4.4 make your site more connected and responsive. Clifford also introduces a new default theme, Twenty Sixteen. Introducing Twenty Sixteen Our newest default theme, Twenty Sixteen, is a modern take [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/anadama-an-example-wordpress-recipe-theme-based-on-react''>WPTavern: Anadama: An Example WordPress Recipe Theme Based on React</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wpweekly-episode-216-wordcamp-us-2015-recap-roundtable''>WPTavern: WPWeekly Episode 216 – WordCamp US 2015 Recap Roundtable</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wp-engine-security-breach-customer-credentials-exposed''>WPTavern: WP Engine Security Breach: Customer Credentials Exposed</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Duplicator</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp&amp;_wpnonce=97b02b2536&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Duplicator''>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
